                In <expan><abbr>ho</abbr><ex>norem</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>omus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ivinae</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Mercurio <lb n="3"/>et Mai<surplus>i</surplus>ae ca<lb break="no" n="4"/>ducium et <lb n="5"/>aram Masc<lb break="no" n="6"/>lius Satto <lb n="7"/><supplied reason="lost">f</supplied>aber ex vo<lb break="no" n="8"/><supplied reason="lost">t</supplied>o <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>aetus</ex></expan> <lb n="9"/><expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Altar, Bekrönung bestoßen und abgeschlagen. Rosettendekor in den pulvini, auf den Nebenseiten Baummotiv.</p>
